  "title": "Data Engineer / Data Analyst",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties & Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Collect, clean, and organise data from construction projects (progress, manpower, equipment, costs)</li><li>Maintain basic databases and structured datasets</li><li>Prepare regular reports and dashboards for management</li><li>Support analysis of productivity, costs, and project performance</li><li>Assist in improving data collection and reporting processes</li><li>Perform any ad hoc tasks as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Data Analytics, Data Science, Computer Science, Engineering, or related fields</li><li>Fresh graduates with a strong interest in the construction industry are welcome to apply.</li><li>Basic knowledge of SQL and Excel (PivotTables, formulas)</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment with good coordination and problem-solving skills.</li><li>Preferably able to start immediately or within short notice.</li></ul>",
